Come with me. Get up!

553
00:56:54,848 --> 00:56:57,760
No, I don't want.

554
00:57:01,768 --> 00:57:05,727
When will I be able to get married?

555
00:57:10,808 --> 00:57:12,764
Get up.

556
00:57:22,888 --> 00:57:24,799
The director is coming.

557
00:57:25,648 --> 00:57:27,639
Hello.

558
00:57:28,888 --> 00:57:30,844
How is the work going?

559
00:57:31,728 --> 00:57:33,798
Everything is fine?

560
00:57:33,848 --> 00:57:35,804
Yes, thank you.

561
00:57:35,888 --> 00:57:41,838
I brought you this present.

562
00:57:42,728 --> 00:57:44,764
Thank you, it's nice.

563
00:57:44,808 --> 00:57:47,686
What is it?

564
00:57:47,768 --> 00:57:50,760
Potatoes.

565
00:57:51,768 --> 00:57:53,838
You like potatoes.

566
00:57:54,688 --> 00:57:56,679
It's very good.

567
00:57:58,648 --> 00:58:01,720
Do you feel good? Isn't it better
than in the hospital?

568
00:58:01,808 --> 00:58:03,764
It's boring here.

569
00:58:03,848 --> 00:58:05,804
Don't say that.

570
00:58:06,688 --> 00:58:10,806
A respectable life seems
boring at first.

571
00:58:11,688 --> 00:58:15,761
But it becomes interesting
once you get into it.

572
00:58:17,808 --> 00:58:19,685
You! How do you do?

573
00:58:19,768 --> 00:58:22,885
Much better...

574
00:58:23,808 --> 00:58:26,686
Thanks to you!

575
00:58:27,768 --> 00:58:30,726
Continue with the consultations.

576
00:58:32,848 --> 00:58:35,760
- Give me a cigarette.
- All right.

577
00:58:38,888 --> 00:58:40,685
Take heart!

578
00:58:41,688 --> 00:58:46,716
You must never let yourself go.

579
00:58:56,848 --> 00:58:58,804
Oh, you're here?

580
00:59:00,688 --> 00:59:02,758
Hello, Mr the Director.

581
00:59:02,848 --> 00:59:05,840
You caused us a lot of troubles.

582
00:59:06,688 --> 00:59:07,803
Forgive me.

583
00:59:08,808 --> 00:59:11,845
- Since when are you here?
- I just arrived.

584
00:59:12,728 --> 00:59:15,800
- I'm happy for you.
- I'm bringing my sister.

585
00:59:16,808 --> 00:59:19,800
- I want her to have her baby here.
- Good idea.

586
00:59:19,888 --> 00:59:25,758
she had some labour pains.
Will she give birth?

587
00:59:28,888 --> 00:59:31,641
Please, I'm counting on you.

588
00:59:38,848 --> 00:59:40,884
Natsuko, pull yourself together.

589
00:59:53,688 --> 00:59:54,803
A bowl! Hot water!

590
00:59:57,728 --> 00:59:59,684
Help me.

591
01:00:01,688 --> 01:00:03,804
She's only 8 months pregnant.
Will it be all right?

592
01:00:03,888 --> 01:00:06,721
The baby wants to get out.

593
01:00:07,808 --> 01:00:11,847
You, stay outside.

594
01:00:30,688 --> 01:00:31,882
Not yet?

595
01:00:34,848 --> 01:00:38,636
You had a child?
How was it?

596
01:00:38,728 --> 01:00:39,683
A great hardship!

597
01:00:39,768 --> 01:00:41,759
You must be happy when it's over...

598
01:00:41,848 --> 01:00:43,804
Yes, when the baby is crying.

599
01:00:43,888 --> 01:00:45,719
Quiet!

600
01:00:48,768 --> 01:00:51,760
Think carefully.

601
01:00:52,888 --> 01:00:57,803
A child is innocent
when he's born.

602
01:00:58,808 --> 01:01:02,847
No matter who the parents are!

603
01:01:04,688 --> 01:01:08,647
Must we degrade such a pure life?

604
01:01:15,768 --> 01:01:19,886
No. Make sure that
it doesn't happen.

605
01:01:20,808 --> 01:01:25,836
Men take advantage of sincere women.

606
01:01:26,808 --> 01:01:29,800
I only think about vengeance.

607
01:01:32,848 --> 01:01:37,717
What did you get out of it?
What's left in you?

608
01:01:37,848 --> 01:01:40,885
A wounded and humiliated woman.

609
01:02:02,768 --> 01:02:05,805
It's done. The mother is fine.

610
01:02:16,728 --> 01:02:17,843
And the baby?

611
01:02:18,888 --> 01:02:24,758
She wasn't fully recovered.
Unfortunately!

612
01:02:34,848 --> 01:02:36,804
I'm sorry, Natsuko.

613
01:02:37,688 --> 01:02:41,681
Maybe it's better this way.

614
01:02:42,728 --> 01:02:47,643
A premature child rarely survives.

615
01:02:48,688 --> 01:02:49,882
I'll have a child.

616
01:02:51,688 --> 01:02:55,761
Next time I'll get married
and I'll have a child.

617
01:03:01,808 --> 01:03:03,719
I'll have one.

618
01:03:06,888 --> 01:03:08,719
You're right.

619
01:03:09,768 --> 01:03:13,761
You'll stay here for a while.

620
01:03:15,648 --> 01:03:20,847
You must not give up hope
even tho you've suffered.

621
01:03:23,768 --> 01:03:27,647
You must become new women.

622
01:03:27,888 --> 01:03:32,882
Not only must you
preserve your body,

623
01:03:33,808 --> 01:03:38,836
but you must also help
to build a better world

624
01:03:39,728 --> 01:03:43,801
where everybody will be happy.

625
01:03:49,848 --> 01:03:51,645
Fusako!

626
01:04:07,768 --> 01:04:12,717
Come spend some time with
a nice girl.

627
01:04:18,768 --> 01:04:21,646
Sir, you look happy.

628
01:04:31,888 --> 01:04:33,879
Sir...

629
01:04:40,888 --> 01:04:44,642
Come quickly.
There's a new girl

630
01:04:44,848 --> 01:04:47,726
- Where is she?
- Near the waste ground.

631
01:04:48,808 --> 01:04:50,799
Fusako! Come quickly!

632
01:04:51,688 --> 01:04:54,725
- Where to?
- To the waste ground over there.

633
01:05:15,848 --> 01:05:17,804
What are you doing?

634
01:05:47,688 --> 01:05:50,839
Where do you come from?
Show yourself.

635
01:05:58,688 --> 01:05:59,757
You!

636
01:06:03,888 --> 01:06:05,765
What's going on?

637
01:06:05,848 --> 01:06:08,840
Nothing. Leave me.

638
01:06:14,768 --> 01:06:18,727
I learned that you ran away
from the house.

639
01:06:18,888 --> 01:06:20,765
It's not good.

640
01:06:20,888 --> 01:06:22,719
I'll go with you.

641
01:06:24,888 --> 01:06:26,799
What about you?

642
01:06:27,848 --> 01:06:30,726
You're the leader
of the whores now?

643
01:06:30,888 --> 01:06:32,765
Leave me!

644
01:06:32,848 --> 01:06:35,681
I'm enjoying my youth.

645
01:06:37,688 --> 01:06:40,760
I've suffered enough already
to be accepted

646
01:06:41,888 --> 01:06:43,799
in your clan.

647
01:06:46,808 --> 01:06:50,767
I spent days at the police station.

648
01:06:51,688 --> 01:06:53,644
Then come!

649
01:06:58,728 --> 01:07:02,880
Do you want to live in this hell?

650
01:07:05,808 --> 01:07:06,877
Come, come over here.

651
01:07:11,808 --> 01:07:16,677
Get sick, lose your sight.

652
01:07:20,848 --> 01:07:24,761
Have your heart and bones rot!

653
01:07:30,808 --> 01:07:33,641
Give birth to a monster.

654
01:07:35,728 --> 01:07:40,722
Destroy all men and women of Japan.

655
01:07:55,728 --> 01:07:57,764
Stupid! Imbecile!

656
01:09:09,808 --> 01:09:10,877
Let's go!

657
01:09:27,888 --> 01:09:29,844
Where are you going Fusako?

658
01:09:31,688 --> 01:09:33,679
You want to leave us?

659
01:09:34,888 --> 01:09:37,641
We'll give you a farewell present.

660
01:09:43,688 --> 01:09:47,727
All right!
Hit me, beat me up.

661
01:09:48,848 --> 01:09:50,804
I've had enough.

662
01:09:52,688 --> 01:09:55,839
Aren't you tired of it?

663
01:09:58,808 --> 01:10:00,639
My dear!

664
01:10:06,688 --> 01:10:10,886
Women must not be like that anymore.

665
01:10:11,728 --> 01:10:12,638
What?

666
01:10:12,888 --> 01:10:15,800
Let's go, help me!

667
01:10:56,808 --> 01:10:58,764
Stop! That's enough!

668
01:11:10,848 --> 01:11:15,638
What's the use of torturing her?

669
01:11:15,808 --> 01:11:20,882
What she said makes us sick.

670
01:11:21,728 --> 01:11:22,843
Let her go.

671
01:11:35,808 --> 01:11:38,641
Go away Fusako.

672
01:11:39,688 --> 01:11:41,679
Don't ever come back.

673
01:11:42,728 --> 01:11:44,798
Have a respectable life.

674
01:11:45,768 --> 01:11:47,759
I don't know what to do...

675
01:11:54,648 --> 01:11:55,763
Fusako!

676
01:12:06,688 --> 01:12:07,757
Let's go.

